  "title": "Brand Growth Specialist (Entry-level)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Excellent ethics and positive learning attitude</li>\n  <li>Leadership potential and ready to take on challenges (view challenges as opportunities instead!)</li>\n  <li>Team player and enjoys interactions with people</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Implementing ethical sales technique with integrity &amp; enthusiasm</li>\n  <li>Lead and drives a team towards a common goal</li>\n  <li>Relationship builder with established clients, customers and consumers</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Benefits:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>One on one MENTORSHIP &amp; SUPPORT system</li>\n  <li>Performance based</li>\n  <li>BUSINESS ADVANCEMENT</li>\n  <li>Highly motivated, FUN and FAMILY-liked environment</li>\n  <li>TRAVELLING opportunities – Regional and International</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Sounds like something you are seeking for?</strong></p>\n<p>Send in your resume to us by clicking APPLY NOW. We will bring you on to a GREATER ADVENTURE! We regret to inform you that only shortlisted candidate will be notified.</p>",
